headline: HR Software Stocks Q3 In Review: Paycom (NYSE:PAYC) Vs Peers
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how hr software stocks fared in Q3, starting with Paycom (NYSE:PAYC).
